Description: Fragment from a black granite statue; inscribed with the prenomen of Osorkon 1 within a cartouche.
Curator's comments: Publication with photos: Helmut Brandl, Kunst und Gesellschaft in der Libyerzeit. Beobachtungen an Königsstatuen der Dritten Zwischenzeit, in: Katalin Anna Kóthay (ed.), Art and Society. Ancient and Modern Contexts of Egyptian Art. Proceedings of the International Conference held at the Museum of Fine Arts, Budapest, 13-15 May 2010, Budapest 2012, pp. 84, 95 (K-4.1), pl. 21, 1a-c.
